codeitall — public surface

This repository contains codeitall's public documentation and API
specification only. It does NOT contain the codeitall substrate, the
ingest/indexer pipeline, or the server source — those are proprietary and
are not redistributed.

Documentation and the OpenAPI specification in this repository may be
referenced and quoted freely (e.g. for integrations and tool catalogs).

The hosted API at https://api.codeitall.dev is free to query under the
documented limits (per-IP key issuance cap and per-key daily quota). No
warranty; provided as-is.

